@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ussbrm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((v2 / (tmp + 0.90 / v2 + 0.49)) / v0)
    tmp = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.99 - v2 + 0.88)) * ((v0 + 0.60 + tmp + 0.37) - 0.92))
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.sin(wp.abs(v0 + 0.70)))
    v0 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.19 / v0 + 0.72)) - (v1 - v2))
    data[tid] = v0
